### 4. OpenAI API Error Handling (open-api.ts)

**Stream Parsing Errors:**
```typescript
try {
    const parsedData: ChatResponse = JSON.parse(cleanedData);
    if (parsedData.error) {
        let errorMessage = '**Error:** ' + (parsedData.error?.message ?? '');
